        "text": "Ars Moriendi: The art of dying",
        "spans": []
      }
    }
  ],
  "body": [
    {
      "key": "text",
      "value": {
        "non-repeat": {
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "content": {
                "text": "What is a good death now?",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 25,
                    "type": "strong",
                    "data": {}
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "\"The woman who lives next door to me is dying. Her bedroom shares a wall with mine and I can hear her: sometimes she watches TV, sometimes she talks to herself, sometimes she is in pain. Her dying presence has necessarily become part of my life.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "\"She is having what most people consider to be a good death: in her own home, surrounded by family, something not everybody is lucky enough to experience.\" Joanna Walsh",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Joanna is spending two weeks at Wellcome Collection, where you can watch her make a drawing based on her work with patients at Sobell House Hospice.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "See photographs of Joanna and the work in progress on Flickr.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 60,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/wellcomecollection/sets/72157626243382062/"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
